#############
### LINUX ###
#############

    --------------------------------------------
    - requirements to build hakuneko on debian -
    --------------------------------------------
    + bash
    + build-essentials (gcc, g++, make, lib*,...)
    + libwxgtk2.8-dev
    + libwxbase2.8-dev

    ----------------------------
    - build & install hakuneko -
    ----------------------------
    # open a terminal
    # change into hakuneko directory
    # run the following commands as root user
    ./configure --prefix=/usr
    make
    make install

    # remove hakuneko
    # run the following command as root user
    make uninstall

    # NOTE: create a source package for redistribution
    # make tgz
    # NOTE: create a debian package for redistribution
    # make deb

#############
### WINNT ###
#############

    ---------------------------------------------
    - Requirements to compile HakuNeko on win32 -
    ---------------------------------------------
    + MinGW32 (GCC >= 4.5)

    ----------------------
    - Compiling HakuNeko -
    ----------------------
    # open a command prompt (cmd)
    # change into hakuneko directory
    # run the following commands
    ./configure --config-mingw32
    # or
    ./configure --config-mingw32-portable
    make
    # binaries can than be found in hakuneko/dist/msw/...
